headline: Is Dow (DOW) Pricing Look Interesting After A 34% One Year Share Price Decline?
summary: If you are wondering whether Dow's share price reflects its true value today, you are not alone. This article is designed to help you make sense of what the current price might be saying. Dow recently closed at US$24.27, with returns of 3.9% over the last 7 days and 5.7% over the last 30 days, while the 1-year return sits at a 34.4% decline and the 3-year and 5-year returns show declines of 47.5% and 45.9% respectively.
